ital_Collections/Revolution/BattlesandSkirmishes.php David C. Munn's scholarly work: ''Battles and skirmishes of the American Revolution in New Jersey'']\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Military history of the United States]]\n[[Category:Militia in the United States| ]]\n[[Category:State defense forces of the United States|*]]\n[[Category:Gun politics in the United States]]\n", "name_user": "Jamietw", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eWar of 1812 (1812\u20131815):typo fix", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Militia_(United_States)"}
