ud of the Year]] (2007) {{small|vs. [[Dave Bautista|Batista]]}}<ref name=WON2010 />\n** [[List of Wrestling Observer Newsletter awards#Match of the Year|Match of the Year]] (2009) {{small|vs. Shawn Michaels at WrestleMania XXV}}<ref name=WON2010 />\n** Match of the Year (2010) {{small|vs. Shawn Michaels at WrestleMania XXVI}}<ref name=WON2010 />\n** [[List of Wrestling Observer Newsletter awards#Worst Match of the Year|Worst Worked Match of the Year]] (2001) {{small|with Kane vs. [[KroniK]] at [[Unforgiven (2001)|Unforgiven]]}}<ref name=WON2010 />\n** Worst Match of the Year (2018) {{small|with Kane vs. Triple H and Shawn Michaels at [[Crown Jewel (2018)|Crown Jewel]]}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.postwrestling.com/2019/03/17/bonus-show-wrestling-observer-newsletter-awards/|title=BONUS SHOW: Wrestling Observer Newsletter Awards|date=March 17, 2019|accessdate=March 23, 2019|work=Post Wrestling}}</ref>\n** [[List of Wrestling Observer Newsletter awards#Most Overrated|Most Overrated]] (2001)<ref name=WON2010 />\n** [[List of Wrestling Observer Newsletter awards#Readers' Least Favorite Wrestler|Readers' Least Favorite Wrestler]] (2001)<ref name=WON2010 />\n** [[List of Wrestling Observer Newsletter awards#Worst Feud of the Year|Worst Feud of the Year]] (1993) {{small|vs. [[Jorge Gonz\u00e1lez (wrestler)|Giant Gonz\u00e1lez]]}}<ref name=WON2010 />\n** [[List of Wrestling Observer Newsletter awards#Most Disgusting Promotional Tactic|Most Disgusting Promotional Tactic]] (2005) {{small|Terrorist angle on [[7 July 2005 London bombings|day of London bombings]]}}<ref name=WON2010 />\n** [[Wrestling Observer Newsletter Hall of Fame]] (Class of 2004)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pwi-online.com/pages/hallofame.html|title=Wrestling Observer Newsletter Hall of Fame|accessdate=January 24, 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Other awards and honors ==\n* Eyegore Award (2000)<ref>{{cite av media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3IqMaa4lKCw|title=THE UNDERTAKER accepts 2000 Eyegore Horror Award 